title: Tuesday Post Show (02-08-22)
itunes:title: Tuesday Post Show (02-08-22)
description:
Bobby on how the Winter Olympics ‘doesn’t feel good’ right now. He also talks about Tom Brady retiring at the height of his career vs. on the way down. We talked to a caller who wanted an update on Raymundo’s parasite. Bobby also reveals what has helped him with his digestive issues and how his dogs are getting along. Bobby shares some big celebrity real estate news. Raymundo and Lunchbox talk about The Tinder Swindler on Netflix.
